http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/CONF20/Confluence+to+PDF?focusedCommentId=148582#comment-148582
explains that an easy way to do this is to add a method in GeneralUtil.  I was wondering if it could be made part of a release.

This method:

private void convertLong(Hashtable table, String key)
    {
        if (table.containsKey(key))
        {
            table.put(key, new Long((String) table.get(key)));
        }
    }

Expects a string, but at least in Perl it's easy to pass some numeric type which makes this fail with a ClassCastException -- perhaps we can accept whaever the other type is?

See https://support.atlassian.com/browse/CSP-2576 for an example perl script.

